d the fact that this sound has already been played into Buffer so that we don't process it again this time around"			SoundJustStarted _ aSound.		] ifFalse:[			"quick start failed; reset the sound so we start over"			aSound reset.		].		ActiveSounds add: aSound].! !!SoundReadoutTile methodsFor: 'arrows' stamp: 'sw 1/28/2005 00:57'!arrowAction: delta	"Do what is appropriate when an arrow on the tile is pressed; delta will be +1 or -1"	| soundChoices index |	soundChoices _ self soundChoices.	index _ soundChoices indexOf: literal.	self literal: (soundChoices atWrap: (index + delta)).	self playSoundNamed: literal! !!SoundReadoutTile methodsFor: 'arrows' stamp: 'sw 11/24/2003 14:54'!handlerForMouseDown: anEvent
